#: ../../language/error_codes/E4213.md:1
msgid "E4213"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4213.md:3
msgid "Compiler diagnostic name: `constr_for_non_struct`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4213.md:5
msgid "Constructor methods can only be defined for `struct` types."
msgstr "构造方法只能为 `struct` 类型定义。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4213.md:7
msgid ""
"MoonBit's `Type::Type` constructor mechanism belongs to structs. Enums, "
"newtypes, and other type forms already have their own construction "
"syntax, so a constructor method for those types is rejected."
msgstr ""
"MoonBit 的 `Type::Type` 构造机制属于结构体。枚举、newtype "
"以及其他类型形式已经有各自的构造语法，因此为这些类型定义构造方法会被拒绝。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4213.md:11
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4213.md:13
msgid ""
"pub enum Status {\n"
"  Ready\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"pub fn Status::Status() -> Status {\n"
"  Ready\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4213.md:17
msgid ""
"`Status` is an `enum`, not a `struct`, so `Status::Status` cannot be used"
" as a struct constructor."
msgstr "`Status` 是 `enum`，不是 `struct`，因此 `Status::Status` 不能用作结构体构造方法。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4213.md:20
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4213.md:22
msgid ""
"Use the enum constructor directly, or change the type to a `struct` if "
"you need a custom constructor method."
msgstr "直接使用枚举构造器；如果确实需要自定义构造方法，则将该类型改为 `struct`。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4213.md:25
msgid ""
"pub struct Status {}\n"
"\n"
"pub fn Status::Status() -> Status {\n"
"  Status::{  }\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

